<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī jayābhyudaya śālivāha 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>na śaka varṣaṁbulu 1478 Agunēṭi 
<lb n="3"/>naḷa saṁvatsara Āṣāḍha ba 13 lu śrīmadrā 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>jādhirāja paramēśvara śrīvīrapratāpa śrī sadā 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>śivadēvamahārāyalu vijayanagaramaṁdu ra 
<lb n="6" break="no"/><unclear>tna</unclear>siṁhvāsanārūḍuḍai pṛthivi sāmrājyaṁ cēyucuṁ 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ḍagānu śivagaṁḍapu<unclear>li</unclear> kaṁtavīrani kumāruḍu vijaya<unclear>na</unclear> 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>garaṁ <unclear>ciṁna</unclear> vīrayyānu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> kaḷyāṇaṁ vīraya koḍuku 
<lb n="9"/>la <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> vīrayya <unclear>ka</unclear>lyāṇaṁ vīrayya [Alluḍu] jaṁjavīrayya 
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> Alluḍu vīrayaku <unclear>pēriṭa</unclear> kaṁbamu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="11"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ramugānu yēkastulai yiccina jaga 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>tāpiguttiśīma <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> gajarāmanipalle 
<lb n="13"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ya samudraṁ śrīmadyakhilāṁ 
<lb n="14" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> yakuṁḍaina <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> rāya <unclear>satraṁ</unclear> rāma 
</p>

<p>Remaining portion of the inscription is badly damaged.</p> 

